title: Significance of The First 10 Minutes In League of Legends Matches.
description: Conducted analysis on professional League of Legends matches played in 2022, focusing on the question of 'how significant is the first 10 minutes of each League of Legends match in regard to gold collected?'

title: Can You Predict An Anime's Score?
description: Collaborated with a team of 5 to attempt to predict the score of an anime on MyAnimeList before it is released by utilizing its genre(s), episode count, adapting studio, streaming platform, and its source material.

title: Rudimentary Messaging Application
description: Collaborated with another student to code a rudimentary coding app similar to Discord and iMessage. Simulated sending and receiving messages by utilizing GUI, SQL, sockets, and multithreading.
